Package: XeniumSpatialAnalysis
Type: Package
Title: Xenium Spatial Analysis Toolkit
Version: 1.0.1
Author: Margarita Kapustina <margokap@student.ubc.ca>
Maintainer: Margarita Kapustina <margokap@student.ubc.ca>
Description: Toolkit in R to perform spatial analysis of Xenium single-cell spatial transcriptomic data, and assess spatial gradients of gene expression. 
